headline: BNY Collaborates with Google Cloud to Advance its Eliza AI Platform with Gemini Enterprise
summary: BNY (NYSE: BK) and Google Cloud today announced the integration of Gemini Enterprise – Google Cloud's agentic AI platform powered by its most advanced models – into BNY's enterprise AI platform, Eliza.
